name: Satanic Void
description: You've been dispatched to the satanic void, the centerpiece in a monumental disaster, as the demons hold earth's population hostage, you tread your way to their realm. Now it's time to bring the fight to their front door, to their land, and make it their blood that is shed. Lock and load. We're going in, and we're gonna come out with a mass causality poll with us, we're gonna make sure those demons taste their own medicine!
